name: Qizziobug 4
description: Cruising down the pixel avenue is Qizziobug #4 - in edition of 4. Bit of a mess with a slight crash that got repaired with a used fender in different colour. Reason could be that it is right-hand-drive, which is rather confusing for driver Tom, who is more of the chaotic sort anyway. But the sky is blue and life is great. http://qizz.io/bugs
